       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">The Sigil Fanguard Beta - Las Vegas 2005</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Fricka</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Aug  2, 2005, 18:05</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=The%20Sigil%20Fanguard%20Beta%20-%20Las%20Vegas%202005&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Fevents%2Farticle_7.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
